Getting the opportunity to witness Music x Crypto x Art x Streetwear come together under one roof seamlessly was an absolutely fascinating experience!

Over the weekend, Johnnie Walker Refreshing Mixer (Non-alcoholic) and SOCIAL organized an exceptional two-day contemporary cultural festival called 'Sauce.'

The goal that lead to organizing SAUCE is all about building a community featuring a creative space that extended past the mundane and intends to unite individuals who share the trait of standing out with their distinctive vision.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Hairfall hacks in the lockdown
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So after spending some time on the Internet and looking out for solutions that’ll help reduce hair fall, I now have few tips & tricks to share with y’all

1- Including foods in your diet which contain essential vitamins are very Important

2- Wash your hair at least twice a week to remove the excess oil & dirt.

3- Remember to always use the right product for your hair as it’s very important.

I personally use the Pantene 2in1 Shampoo + Conditioner☺️ @pantene_india 
So guys, I tried these tips for 14 days straight and I could see a noticeable reduction in my hair fall.
Watch the video and check out more such tips and let me know in the comments below if you see a change too!❤️

latestPosts.caption:
35 years of togetherness <3
I’ve watched you both choose each other, over and over again, not just in the easy moments but in the hardest ones too. Love like yours isn’t just about grand gestures or perfect days; it’s in the small, quiet things.
the way you show up for each other, the way you fight and still find your way back, the way you make a life together feel like home.

You’ve taught me that real love isn’t just about finding the right person, but about choosing them, even when things aren’t perfect. You are my greatest example of what love should be, and because of you, I know I will never settle for anything less.

Happy 35 years, Mom and Dad. Your love is my favorite love story 🫀
